Package net.vivialconnect.model.message

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Attachment
    A MMS can contains attachments, which can be a media, text or any supported object by the API defined in the following link: https://dashboard.vivialconnect.net/docs/mms-media-types
    AttachmentCollection
    Wrapper class for map the collection of attachments returned by the API.
    BulkInfo  
    BulkInfoCollection
    Wrapper class for map a collection of bulk send jobs returned by the API.
    BulkMessage
    Bulk requests allow you to enqueue a large number of messages using only a few requests.
    Message
    Sending messages is the main feature provide by the Vivial Connect API.
    MessageCollection
    Wrapper class for map a list of messages returned by the API.
